{
  "sn51.28:0.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51 ",
  "sn51.28:0.2": "3. Ayoguḷavagga ",
  "sn51.28:0.3": "28. Dutiyaānandasutta ",
  "sn51.28:1.1": "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: ",
  "sn51.28:1.2": "“katamā nu kho, ānanda, iddhi, katamo iddhipādo, katamā iddhipādabhāvanā, katamā iddhipādabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā”ti? ",
  "sn51.28:1.3": "Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā bhagavaṃnettikā …pe…. ",
  "sn51.28:2.1": "“Idhānanda, bhikkhu anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti—ekopi hutvā bahudhā hoti …pe… yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteti—",
  "sn51.28:2.2": "ayaṃ vuccatānanda, iddhi. ",
  "sn51.28:3.1": "Katamo cānanda, iddhipādo? ",
  "sn51.28:3.2": "Yo, ānanda, maggo yā paṭipadā iddhilābhāya iddhipaṭilābhāya saṃvattati—",
  "sn51.28:3.3": "ayaṃ vuccatānanda, iddhipādo. ",
  "sn51.28:4.1": "Katamā cānanda, iddhipādabhāvanā? ",
  "sn51.28:4.2": "Idhānanda, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, ",
  "sn51.28:4.3": "vīriyasamādhi …pe… ",
  "sn51.28:4.4": "cittasamādhi … ",
  "sn51.28:4.5": "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti—",
  "sn51.28:4.6": "ayaṃ vuccatānanda, iddhipādabhāvanā. ",
  "sn51.28:5.1": "Katamā cānanda, iddhipādabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā? ",
  "sn51.28:5.2": "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—",
  "sn51.28:5.3": "sammādiṭṭhi …pe… sammāsamādhi—",
  "sn51.28:5.4": "ayaṃ vuccatānanda, iddhipādabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā”ti. ",
  "sn51.28:5.5": "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
}